channel.title: Titania - Looking for a good Client Developer
channel.description:
[center][b][size=18pt]Titania[/size][/b][/center]
Hello, this topic is about Titania RSPS looking for a Client Developer. So far me and my friend Ali have been working on a Near-Reality remake. So far it's been going pretty well, but as neither of us liked Client sided stuff I decided to do it. I done fairly well but I don't think I'm putting as much into the server as I could.
[b]Positions Needed:[/b]
[s]1 Client developer[/s]
[b]Media:[/b]
We will be going a long way with this as already we've put a lot of effort into it. If you are interested here is some pictures of what you'll be joining so far:
[img]http://i1330.photobucket.com/albums/w561/brandonharkness13/TitaniaV4_zps075c228e.png[/img] [img]http://i1330.photobucket.com/albums/w561/brandonharkness13/TitaniaV3_zps20935058.png[/img] [img]http://i1330.photobucket.com/albums/w561/brandonharkness13/Titaniav2_zps6ec13824.png[/img] [img]http://i1330.photobucket.com/albums/w561/brandonharkness13/TitaniaV1_zpsebf6a519.png[/img] [img]http://i1330.photobucket.com/albums/w561/brandonharkness13/TitaniaV5_zps018a50ad.png[/img]
If you are interested in joining fill in the form below:
[code] Age: Are you on daily?: How long are you on each day?: Experience?: Proof of previous work?: Skype?: Will you stay dedicated?: [/code]
